Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽的  早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是绝赞的中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦  赏雪温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我冲热水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜小夜  堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先进浴池里来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫  好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快镇静点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极乐极乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完星星之后果然还是要这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过附近居然有这么好的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  虽然旅馆里的澡堂也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是开放感就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了如果不好好泡一下要死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天结果还是变成了游戏大会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为黎明的时候天气才好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要回去了  只好赌一下今晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天其实也没怎么看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  我们也做了一样的事  不能只顾着说别人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一年级的夏季合宿吧  三波为了买坚果擅自外出…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了去找她和她一起被困在雾中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只有我们两人的夏日的山里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}当时的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当时学姐们也是发射了波动炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到江户川同学点闪光灯才想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一年的  天气一直不好  所以就对着云打着玩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边谈论着萌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想来  我们现在所走的路就是从那时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波动炮…就作为我们高见女中天文部的传统吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…只是随便想出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小蓬蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是必须要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方商店也都是很远的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜不穿衣服显得更丰满  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且皮肤光滑得像鸡蛋一样  可以让我摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是说  已经在摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小星见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和想的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个  小蓬蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们…她们绝对是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是在引诱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此偷看吧…就去偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她们这样  就去偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说别露出身体啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  草哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们那边浴池怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后洗了吗  毛巾有拿过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  美星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生不要偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  江户川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要拦着我  大八木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要连肩膀都泡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是糟透了  真的完了  绝对完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习用脑之后要补充糖份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  路万同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  这个这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总整理  检查  读了这本书就能及格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  很适合现在的总复习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能多陪陪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是准备考试的学生  就算吃顿饭也没什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说已经预约好饭店了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是近江小姐的预约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是我经常和家人一起来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药膳汤和香粥…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没吃得这么饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我想着如果慢慢吃应该能吃完的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要关门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然待了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对  是今天的主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到  还不可以把手拿开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把手拿开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家饭店的露天座位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然冬天不开放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我硬请他们为我们开放的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有街灯…用望远镜的话应该能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大犬座的脚延伸出去  靠近地平线的红色星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老人星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(330,435)}Canopus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还担心如果看不到怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我还是第一次看到真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你哦  感觉你在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也不怎么有不勉强也没关系的应试学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也不用承受过重的压力连饭也吃不下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路万同学的话  只要放松一些  注意身体的话就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  趁着还不冷的时候回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间也不早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  近江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么对我这么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…想要我来说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到春天之后…再慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮完全…落山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影班在营地周边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适当的移动位置是可以的  不过不要离开太远拍摄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里在天文台里继续录影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的最后一天  各自完成成果的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:02.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}多么肯花钱  一人一台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于摄影部的协助  尽可能借多来了相机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样拼命加油的话好感度就会up了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  我现在就给大家做甜酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白冬天如果冷的话  就能看到这么多星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市中就只能看到明亮的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某种意义上来说星座也比较容易连起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种能看得蛮清楚的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户座的一等星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(280,435)}Orion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色的参宿四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(351,435)}Betelgeuse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小犬座的南河三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(361,435)}Procyon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大犬座的天狼星连成的冬季大三角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(300,435)}Sirius
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后猎户座的参宿七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(300,435)}Orion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(381,435)}Rigel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金牛座的毕宿五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(361,435)}Aldebaran
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御夫座的五车二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(360,435)}Capella
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上双子座的北河三就组成了冬季的大六角形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(280,435)}Pollux
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为已经看惯了…原来是完全不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为冬天有7颗一等星  所以很好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}木乃伊型睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星确实很明亮  空气感觉也不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空好像更暗一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是错觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天太阳落山早  所以首先没有太阳残照的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且空气乾燥  透明度更高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天  在城市里时常能看到清晰得令人惊讶的闪亮星星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明亮的星星  黑暗的天幕  高透明度的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如此  才能看到这清晰的光辉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过像今天这样的日子有点不适合用望远镜看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明闪烁得这么亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  这样星光闪烁的夜晚上空的气流不安定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的闪烁  和透明度没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会因为大气的晃动而影响成像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如晃动的水面不容易看清水底一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不晃动的话就能看得很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在天文台里做影片摄影也是因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅气流起伏摇曳也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能把视野好的图像挑选出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此还是要看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  冬天能通过双筒或者小口径望远镜看到很多有趣的散开星团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个晚上都会很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  小朔  昴宿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从奥利安追逐乱逃的美女姐妹好萌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(218,435)}Orion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来向M35出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M35
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的来源是萌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之我也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's星景拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这个要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:57.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞吞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时都是交给江户川弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的  别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个三脚架再放低点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快门钢丝顶针放这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有带怀炉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀炉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是一次性的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把用桐灰的怀炉放在相机这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样镜片就不会有水雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在户外用品店就有得卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an9}准备完善的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}怀炉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an7}结\N实\N的\N三\N脚\N架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  来休息一下怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喝甜酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小酒井做的甜酒  今年也是最后一次喝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的是最好喝的  小酒井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三波同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说小酒井你还不结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌讨厌  不要说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们就要离开了  好不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有学姐们的话  我还能带动大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好  你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果是你们大家的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着高见女子高校的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的觉得大家都各得其乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(100,100,\alpha&H00&)}之{\r}{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(200,200,\alpha&H00&)}类{\r}{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(300,300,\alpha&H00&)}的{\r}{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(400,400,\alpha&H00&)}…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以杏同学就按你自己的做法做一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说我们自己比较需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有望远镜  没有新生入部的话就会变成同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个部不知明年还存不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  虽然不知道你在不安些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我知道杏同学很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相沢也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  别让人这么痛切嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小星见  有什么想看的天体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  还没有看过土星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然视野还有点不好  要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我记得上次他们好像说想用自己的望远镜来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是什么  目镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西也很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有目镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这到处贴满的标签是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星  那该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得吗  我们还一起在上面乱画过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本体  在事故的时候已经坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有目镜能带来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想带些东西跟大家一起分享
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是土星  因为也是爸爸喜欢的天体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起看我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和狮子座恰好重合的就是土星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗七星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大角星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(320,435)}Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角宿一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(320,435)}Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起看过的春天的星星也开始可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空转了一圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星与星连结起来季节的接力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又开始新一轮的接力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得  也试试导入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come come  朔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和这里调动一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  不是这里？ 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名流了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事  冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入画面了就调整焦距
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样  看的到光环吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多亏了目镜的关系吗  很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然视野一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是摇摇曳曳小小的映像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小  不过好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有光环
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟伽利略号的图一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(289,435)}Galileo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这宇宙感是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白大家为什么想看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离太阳第六近的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少人亲眼看过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把这份感动像这样传递才有了现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也  想传递下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小星见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要在春天到来的时候  在新的地方把这份感动传递下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  或许我还不够可靠  不过我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  多亏了你  今天很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣的各位也谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给下一次轮回的星星  鸣礼炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极乐极乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿果然少不了这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那声音…你们的稿子有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  有在好好写啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年开始就是二年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为文艺部员要更加好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来学姐  那是竹筒敲石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的天空之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这许多接力传递下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为新生马上就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不引人注目一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此你也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路万部长考上了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天开始要和近江学姐一起过校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们各自都升了一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里也来了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后天文部为了存续问题努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员最少也要拉一个进来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承路万部长  我被任命为部长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明野美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也要竭尽全力出击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜学姐来当应该比较好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最热情的可是美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  拉一个人没什么难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  江户川  认真一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经被分到别的班级去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连社团活动也没了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  我跟你不是一个班了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们是天文部三人组了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到隔壁班去找你玩可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的一句话我就能够好好努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小朔  那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…虽然去年有时也发一些壁报
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想今年应该更努力一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创刊号加上募集部员的传单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好  这很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看一下  我们是天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天文部  给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天文部…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:23:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想让你们部存续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜第二次连任会长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.07,0:24:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是浪费  难得能写出这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚前辈在夸奖文章
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去做你们该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.72,0:24:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我还没有给你屋顶的使用权啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.57,0:24:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部正在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员大大大大大招募中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起来  看星星
